435
00:30:46,010 --> 00:30:47,890
I'm not sure about that.

436
00:30:48,460 --> 00:30:50,329
Your Highness, you mean...?

437
00:30:50,329 --> 00:30:53,229
Brother, go get the recruitment record of Qianzhou Army

438
00:30:53,230 --> 00:30:55,910
