463
00:32:55,830 --> 00:33:01,799
Well, please take care of the case and make further investigation.

464
00:33:01,800 --> 00:33:03,279
But I'm telling you.

465
00:33:03,280 --> 00:33:04,709
What's faked can't be true.

466
00:33:04,710 --> 00:33:07,919
You'll find out something.

467
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:13,350
Minister Han, His Majesty has drafted a decree

468
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:15,709
